  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39940842_11_1245-1292",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "1245-1292",
      "markText": "所谓幸福，或许指的便是明明置身幸福却对幸福恍若不觉，就这样在琐碎无害的牢骚中度过平凡的每一天。",
      "totalCount": 8657,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39940842&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1245&rangeEnd=1292",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/21c32850726172ea21c0ac3?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1245&rangeEnd=1292"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39940842_11_10468-10541",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "10468-10541",
      "markText": "人生的最后一程，我不愿在意他人的看法，只盼独自消磨，而后永远离开。这是因为我尚且保留着某种傲慢的尊严，不愿意让任何人看见自己孱弱得不堪一击的模样。",
      "totalCount": 3568,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39940842&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=10468&rangeEnd=10541",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/21c32850726172ea21c0ac3?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=10468&rangeEnd=10541"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39940842_11_1158-1188",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "1158-1188",
      "markText": "能够理所当然地相信自己“拥有明日”，实在是格外幸福的一件事。",
      "totalCount": 3285,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39940842&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1158&rangeEnd=1188",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/21c32850726172ea21c0ac3?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1158&rangeEnd=1188"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39940842_11_7077-7172",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "7077-7172",
      "markText": "在这边的人看来是出口，在对面的人眼中却是入口。我想，无论生还是死，同样具有深刻的意义。我们所有人都处在生命的循环之中，并且不断改变着自己的形貌。追根究底，这个循环里不存在所谓的开始与终结。”",
      "totalCount": 3196,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39940842&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=7077&rangeEnd=7172",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/21c32850726172ea21c0ac3?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=7077&rangeEnd=7172"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39940842_11_1612-1664",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "1612-1664",
      "markText": "世上还有一个人，用这样的方式，对我翘首以待。仅凭这一点，我便觉得自己能够渡过这道人生最大亦是最后的难关。",
      "totalCount": 2988,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39940842&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1612&rangeEnd=1664",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/21c32850726172ea21c0ac3?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1612&rangeEnd=1664"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39940842_12_5689-5721",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "5689-5721",
      "markText": "“将不幸一口气吸入肺腑，再化为感激呼出，你的人生终会闪闪发光。”",
      "totalCount": 2772,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39940842&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=5689&rangeEnd=5721",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/21c32850726172ea21c0ac3?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=5689&rangeEnd=5721"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39940842_11_4885-4953",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "4885-4953",
      "markText": "新鲜空气如雪崩一般源源不断地涌至肺底。哪怕只是为了品尝这里的空气，也值得来到柠檬岛。那种感觉，好像整个肺部被干净的空气从内到外地清洗过。",
      "totalCount": 2431,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39940842&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=4885&rangeEnd=4953",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/21c32850726172ea21c0ac3?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=4885&rangeEnd=4953"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39940842_11_18220-18278",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "18220-18278",
      "markText": "确实，客观来看，这段生命过于短暂，可若要说长，仍是足够漫长的一生。即便不及珠穆朗玛峰雄伟，它也尽力容纳过山川与谷涧。",
      "totalCount": 2272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39940842&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=18220&rangeEnd=18278",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/21c32850726172ea21c0ac3?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=18220&rangeEnd=18278"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39940842_13_3945-4001",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "3945-4001",
      "markText": "“没有一件事，是白费力气。 “没有一件事，是毫无意义。”",
      "totalCount": 2240,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39940842&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=3945&rangeEnd=4001",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/21c32850726172ea21c0ac3?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=3945&rangeEnd=4001"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39940842_14_14940-15007",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "14940-15007",
      "markText": "我从未想过，这些平淡无奇的日常生活会变成格外珍贵的记忆，而有朝一日，所有天真烂漫的时光都会令人无比眷恋，以至于我想将它们紧紧拥在怀中。",
      "totalCount": 2144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39940842&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=14940&rangeEnd=15007",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/21c32850726172ea21c0ac3?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=14940&rangeEnd=15007"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39940842_14_14403-14426",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "14403-14426",
      "markText": "人啊，不是因为快乐才笑，而是因为笑才变得快乐。",
      "totalCount": 2115,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39940842&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=14403&rangeEnd=14426",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/21c32850726172ea21c0ac3?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=14403&rangeEnd=14426"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39940842_11_13945-14010",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "13945-14010",
      "markText": "因为除了自己，我已一无所有。我不会结婚，也不会有小孩，更无法向父母求助，连离世的衣服都不得不亲自挑选。终究不会有人来为我做这一切。",
      "totalCount": 2112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39940842&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=13945&rangeEnd=14010",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/21c32850726172ea21c0ac3?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=13945&rangeEnd=14010"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39940842_11_7992-8066",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "7992-8066",
      "markText": "然而如今，我再也没有精力了。无论愤怒，抑或哭泣，甚至空欢喜，我都已厌倦，不想为一切无用的情绪耗费心神。感情的爆发意味着削弱生命，对此我有切实的体会。",
      "totalCount": 2072,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39940842&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=7992&rangeEnd=8066",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/21c32850726172ea21c0ac3?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=7992&rangeEnd=8066"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39940842_13_9547-9561",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "9547-9561",
      "markText": "眼泪不是表达悲伤的唯一方式。",
      "totalCount": 1926,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39940842&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=9547&rangeEnd=9561",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/21c32850726172ea21c0ac3?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=9547&rangeEnd=9561"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39940842_12_3453-3487",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "3453-3487",
      "markText": "武雄先生的视线久久凝在那碗豆花上，仿佛在观看一部令人怀念的无声电影。",
      "totalCount": 1904,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39940842&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=3453&rangeEnd=3487",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/21c32850726172ea21c0ac3?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=3453&rangeEnd=3487"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39940842_11_19449-19504",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "19449-19504",
      "markText": "我习惯优先揣度对方的情绪，牺牲自己的感受，以讨得对方欢心。长久以来我都深信，自己的幸福源于他人对我展露的笑容。",
      "totalCount": 1859,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39940842&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=19449&rangeEnd=19504",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/21c32850726172ea21c0ac3?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=19449&rangeEnd=19504"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39940842_13_6539-6577",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "6539-6577",
      "markText": "志麻奶奶说：“活着是件非常难得的事，因此遇见好吃的东西，要面带笑容地品尝。”",
      "totalCount": 1736,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39940842&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=6539&rangeEnd=6577",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/21c32850726172ea21c0ac3?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=6539&rangeEnd=6577"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39940842_11_12699-12755",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "12699-12755",
      "markText": "虽然我也体会了恋爱的滋味，可是既不曾惊天动地地爱过，也不曾痛彻肺腑地失去，从这个层面来讲，我的人生简直平凡至极。",
      "totalCount": 1728,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39940842&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=12699&rangeEnd=12755",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/21c32850726172ea21c0ac3?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=12699&rangeEnd=12755"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39940842_11_28515-28540",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "28515-28540",
      "markText": "人生就是如此，不打开盖子，永远不知道里面藏着什么。",
      "totalCount": 1710,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=39940842&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=28515&rangeEnd=28540",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/21c32850726172ea21c0ac3?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=28515&rangeEnd=28540"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "39940842_11_20049-20071",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "20049-20071",
      "markText": "对中意的事物，说喜欢；对讨厌的事物，说厌烦。",
      "totalCount": 1617,
